  <expertsContent><![CDATA[<p>We know a thing or two about ski &amp; snowboarding holidays - we’ve been taking people skiing since <a data-udi="umb://document/82a77c25f84a48e383e2c0435488ddd8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/82a77c25f84a48e383e2c0435488ddd8}" title="History" class="ski-air-color">Walter Ingham</a> took his first group to Austria 90 years ago – and we’re just as passionate about sharing our love of the mountains today.</p>
<p>Take your pick from premium <a data-udi="umb://document/31c3c6181bb642ffab4ba3d3f4762c55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/31c3c6181bb642ffab4ba3d3f4762c55}" title="Hotels">hotels</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257}" title="Chalets">chalets</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/8ffc82b2f62046538c164fffbcdb7693" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8ffc82b2f62046538c164fffbcdb7693}" title="Apartments (Self-catering)">apartments</a> in our favourite snow-sure resorts across Europe and Canada, with a range of regional travel options and transfers to resort included. We know <a data-udi="umb://document/e0c616470b3c42db8e6ecca08307cca1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0c616470b3c42db8e6ecca08307cca1}" title="When to go" class="ski-air-color">when to go</a> to which resorts and keep you up to date throughout the season with our <a data-udi="umb://document/3464b8f6fd3f41d9b286f0b64dac2b79" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3464b8f6fd3f41d9b286f0b64dac2b79}" title="Snow">weekly snow forecast</a>. We have a <a data-udi="umb://document/7dec408f2e7c459ab8c303a08bc1c68d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7dec408f2e7c459ab8c303a08bc1c68d}" title="Ski Holiday Types" class="ski-air-color">ski holiday type</a> to suit you and also offer a <a data-udi="umb://document/f4ae07b2d50a4681918f9b4a3d6500c6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f4ae07b2d50a4681918f9b4a3d6500c6}" title="Snow Guarantee">snow guarantee</a> for those in need of reassurance when booking this winter. You can now get to some of the top ski resorts in Europe by <a data-udi="umb://document/599491ab41f44d11a3c4cd9f7ef48bf5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/599491ab41f44d11a3c4cd9f7ef48bf5}" title="Ski holidays by train">train</a>.</p>
<p>From the thrill-seekers to the après skiers, our expert team will be with you at every turn.</p>]]></expertsContent>
